				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><table class="infobox biography vcard" cellspacing="3" style="border-spacing: 3px; width:22em;">
<tr>
<th colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; font-size:125%; font-weight:bold;"><span class="fn">Michael Cimino</span></th>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left;">Born</th>
<td class="" style=""><span style="display:none">(<span class="bday">1939-02-03</span>)</span> February 3, 1939 <span class="noprint ForceAgeToShow">(age&#160;74)</span><br />
<span class="birthplace">New York City, New York, United States</span></td>
</tr>
<tr class="">
