</tr>
</table>
<p><b>Michael Cimino</b> (<span class="nowrap"><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA"><a href="Help_IPA_for_English" title="Help:IPA for English">/</a></span><span class="IPA"><a href="Help_IPA_for_English#Key" title="Help:IPA for English"><span title="/tʃ/ 'ch' in 'china'" style="border-bottom:1px dotted">tʃ</span></a></span><span class="IPA"><a href="Help_IPA_for_English#Key" title="Help:IPA for English"><span title="/ɪ/ short 'i' in 'bid'" style="border-bottom:1px dotted">ɪ</span></a></span><span class="IPA"><a href="Help_IPA_for_English#Key" title="Help:IPA for English"><span title="/ˈ/ primary stress follows" style="border-bottom:1px dotted">ˈ</span></a></span><span class="IPA"><a href="Help_IPA_for_English#Key" title="Help:IPA for English"><span title="'m' in 'my'" style="border-bottom:1px dotted">m</span></a></span><span class="IPA"><a href="Help_IPA_for_English#Key" title="Help:IPA for English"><span title="/iː/ long 'e' in 'bead'" style="border-bottom:1px dotted">iː</span></a></span><span class="IPA"><a href="Help_IPA_for_English#Key" title="Help:IPA for English"><span title="'n' in 'nigh'" style="border-bottom:1px dotted">n</span></a></span><span class="IPA"><a href="Help_IPA_for_English#Key" title="Help:IPA for English"><span title="/oʊ/ long 'o' in 'bode'" style="border-bottom:1px dotted">oʊ</span></a></span><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA"><a href="Help_IPA_for_English" title="Help:IPA for English">/</a></span></span> <span title="English pronunciation respelling" class="Unicode"><a href="Wikipedia_Pronunciation_respelling_key" title="Wikipedia:Pronunciation respelling key"><i>chi-<b><span class="smallcaps"><span class="SMALLCAPS" style="FONT-VARIANT:SMALL-CAPS;"><span class="NOCAPS" style="TEXT-TRANSFORM:LOWERCASE;">MEE</span></span></span></b>-noh</i></a></span>;<sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup> born February 3, 1939) is an American <a href="Film_director" title="Film director">film director</a>, <a href="Screenwriter" title="Screenwriter">screenwriter</a>, producer and author. He is best known for directing, producing and co-writing the 1978 <a href="Academy_Award" title="Academy Award">Academy Award</a>-winning film <i><a href="The_Deer_Hunter" title="The Deer Hunter">The Deer Hunter</a></i>, and for writing and directing the infamous 1980 film <i><a href="Heaven's_Gate_(film)" title="Heaven's Gate (film)">Heaven's Gate</a></i>.</p>
