<li id="cite_note-Wakeman-9"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Wakeman_9-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Wakeman_9-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Wakeman_9-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">Wakeman, John (1988). <i>World Film Directors</i> (2). The H. W. Wilson Company. pp. 214-219.</span></li>
